		Harder to play &quot;evil&quot; on a roleplay server?		
	</tr>
	
	
		<tr align="left" valign="top" class="BoardRowA">
			<td class="BoardRowA" rowspan=3 width="17%">
			<a href="/user.asp?usr=92335" class="AuthorLink">Quillion_the_Gnome_needs_ign_merge$$$</a>&nbsp;<a href="/help/default.asp?goto=faqs%2Easp%23stars"><img align=absmiddle src=http://media.ign.com/boardimages/star.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="189 posts"></a><br> 
