			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				Until FV gets PVP, there really isnt a real way to RP evil. <br>  <br> The Play nice rules should not apply when a dispute between good and evil. Since when did evil, who is out for themselves, decide it would be a good idea to share kills? <br> Evils would either, watch the creatures wipe out the goods and laugh about it, or buff the monsters to watch them kill the goods. <br>  <br> Evil doesnt help good unless its some catastrophic event that will affect their own way of living. <br>  <br> There are no &quot;camps&quot; in role playing. If for some reason you need a particular item though, and run into someone else there for the same item, it should be a KS fest between good and evil since they both want the same item first. <br>  <br> 
