			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				While technically, kill stealing is not against the rules, this is still a game and I won't lower myself to do that. Just because I am an evil race doesnt mean my mission is to ruin every light race players fun. <br>  <br> Buffing mobs btw, is against the rules and is an offence where you can receive a warning and other penalties. <br>  <br> I disagee about evil races not being able to roleplay just because this server isnt pvp. There is a difference between ROLEPLAYING and PLAYING. <br>  <br> When we are ROLEPLAYING, we are interacting with other people in a fashion that suits are alignment. When we are PLAYING we are following a rulest created for us by the game designers. <br>  <br> I understand this is not a pvp server. Thats even more of a reason for the light and dark races to play by the rules. Just because this is a roleplay server doesnt mean we shouldn't practice some common sense when it comes to playing. <br> 
